hcc_text: West Kingsbridge Road is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At West Kingsbridge Road at Reservoir Avenue and Aqueduct Avenue West, there was 1 severe injury in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
